quran[12]{c,v,t}:
  22,11,"Ndetse no mu bantu hari ugaragira Allah ashidikanya. Iyo icyiza kimugezeho aratuza, naho yagerwaho n’ikigeragezo agasubira mu buhakanyi (nyuma y’uko yari yarayobotse); ubwo akaba ahombye (ibyiza byo ku) isi n’imperuka. Icyo ni cyo gihombo kigaragara"
  22,12,Asenga ibitari Allah bitagira icyo bimutwara cyangwa ngo bigire icyo bimumarira. Uko ni ko kuyoba guhambaye (kutagira igaruriro)
  22,13,"Asenga icyo inabi yacyo iri hafi kurusha ineza yacyo, kandi rwose (ibyo bihitiyemo kugaragira bitari Allah) ni byo barinzi babi ndetse bikaba n’inshuti mbi"
  22,14,"Mu by’ukuri ba bandi bemeye bakanakora ibikorwa byiza, Allah azabinjiza mu busitani butembamo imigezi (Ijuru), kuko rwose Allah akora ibyo ashaka"
  22,15,"Uwo ari we wese wibwira ko Allah atazatabara (Intumwa Muhamadi) kuri iyi si ndetse no ku munsi w’imperuka, namanike umugozi ku gisenge maze awushyire mu ijosi, narangiza awuce (yiyahure) maze arebe ko umugambi we (mubisha) ukuraho uburakari bwe"
  22,16,"Uko ni na ko twahishuye imirongo isobanutse (igitabo cya Qur’an), kandi Allah ayobora uwo ashaka"
  22,17,"Mu by’ukuri ba bandi bemeye (Allah n’intumwa ye Muhamadi), Abayahudi (abemeye ubutumwa bwa Musa ku gihe cye), Abaswaabi’i (abagumye kuri kamere yabo batagize idini bayoboka), Abanaswara [abemeye ubutumwa bwa Issa (Yesu) ku gihe cye], Abamajusi (abasenga umuriro) ndetse n’abasenga ibindi bitari Allah; rwose Allah azabakiranura ku munsi w’imperuka. Mu by’ukuri Allah ni Umuhamya uhebuje wa buri kintu"
  22,18,"Ese ntubona ko ibiri mu birere n’ibiri ku isi, izuba, ukwezi, inyenyeri, imisozi, ibiti, ibiremwa byose bigenda ku isi ndetse na benshi mu bantu byubamira Allah? Ariko abenshi (mu bantu batamwubamira) bakwiye ibihano. Kandi uwo Allah yasuzuguje ntawamwubahisha, kuko mu by’ukuri Allah akora ibyo ashaka"
  22,19,"Aya matsinda abiri (abemeramana n’abahakanyi) ntiyavuze rumwe kuri Nyagasani wayo; bityo ba bandi bahakanye bazadoderwa imyambaro ikozwe mu muriro, maze basukwe amazi yatuye mu mitwe"
  22,20,(Ayo mazi yatuye) azayengesha ibyo mu nda zabo ndetse n’impu zabo
  22,21,Kandi bazahondeshwa inyundo z’ibyuma
  22,22,"Buri uko bazajya bashaka kuwuvamo kubera ububabare, bazajya bawusubizwamo; maze (babwirwe bati) “Ngaho nimusogongere ibihano bitwika.”"